beer.beer_description:
There's nothing like a good cup of tea...

Simple, comforting, and an all-round crowd-pleaser. Sur, you might have your tea with milk, or prefer herbal over an Earl Grey, but all tea is made equal. We are loud and proud when it comes to equality no matter what your cup of tea is.

With a bright hue and zesty tropical hit - EQUALItea is a soul-soothing drop to ponder life and how we can make it better for all. Enjoy!
